8766 |         R_FED_DEF_TAX_DR_NOLS_AMT(0)=SUM(R_FED_DEF_TAX_DR_NOLS_AMT(1:))|
8767 |         R_BTL_TAXABLE_REVENUES(0) = SUM(R_BTL_TAXABLE_REVENUES(1:))|
