8769 |         R_FEDERAL_BTL_TAXABLE_INCOME(0) =|
8770 |     +                             SUM(R_FEDERAL_BTL_TAXABLE_INCOME(1:))|
8771 |         R_FEDERAL_BTL_INCOME_TAX(0)= SUM(R_FEDERAL_BTL_INCOME_TAX(1:))|
8772 |C|
