8774 |C|
8775 |         CALL ACTUAL_MONTHLY_INCOME_TAX_ITEMS(R_YR,R_CLASS,|
8776 |     +                                        R_FEDERAL_INCOME_TAXES,|
8777 |     +                                        FED_TAX_CODE)|
